<subSubSection pageId="9" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,151,1328]" pageId="9">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,397,439,464]" pageId="9">Studied material</emphasis>
. Eight specimens observed alive (squash method) and eight (MUSM 3406–3413) specimens fixed in polyvinyl–lactophenol.
</paragraph>
